replies.body:
I'm certainly no developer, but I can definitely help you resolve this issue. Most of the time, crashes during matchmaking is caused by your client losing connection to the matchmaking servers. I recommend you first ensure your local network settings are compatible with League by working through our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if those steps caused any change.
